{"tid":1148330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普聲稱 已展開徵收餘下$2.54萬億中國貨25%關稅程序","createTime":"2019-05-10T11:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T12:03:05.000Z","uid":179908,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b935879213b9bc736e8e2e4d10968ab96c1b280e","tid":1148330,"uid":179908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"特朗普在社交網指，已展開向餘下3,250億美元（2.54萬億港元）中國貨徵收25%關稅的程序，稱關稅可令美國庫房可多收1,000億美元，當中的150億美元可以用於購買美國農產品，遠多於中國的購買金額，另外的850億美元則可用於新的基建或醫療等用途。特朗普指與中國的談判以「友好的態度」繼續，但強調毋須着急，目前談判會繼續，希望中方不會再次改動協議。"},{"pid":"bfb15cd16f3a6a8c767fb8824293872895f2222c","tid":1148330,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/05/10/Zs3qrp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F05%2F10%2FZs3qrp.png&h=cb497597&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f54aabf706705a1218aefb687885394eeb39f81","tid":1148330,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ea06213b245d2bcc42b9fc74dc5cbdfba382481","tid":1148330,"uid":129030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f54aabf706705a1218aefb687885394eeb39f81","tid":1148330,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"Sleepy Joe Biden"}]}